  "text": "## Executive Summary  \nFirstUK Bank operates 12 branches across the United Kingdom, strategically located to serve customer bases in major metropolitan areas and regional centers. Branches provide full banking services including account opening, customer service, and cash handling.  \n**Total Branches:** 12\n**Total Branch Staff:** 12 (1–2 per branch)\n**Head Office:** London\n**Service Hours:** Monday–Friday 09:00–17:00, Saturday 09:00–13:00  \n---",
